ExpertQueryJsonObject - Class in msquerybuilderbackend.entity
entity class for the ExpertQueryJsonObject objects with getter and setter ExpertQueryJsonObject objects are like ExpertQuery objects but are only used for the frontend because of the handling with categories The frontend keeps just the unique name of the category while in the neo4j database (ExpertQuery objects) the category is a relationship
